{"tid":544122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天津IMAX銀幕遭割毀 價值40~60萬人民幣","createTime":"2018-01-29T08:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T11:22:47.000Z","uid":75969,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9b47974768fd599419bed217411a906a79ff6b3c","tid":544122,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180129/640_5505a50684d1a927f7f7a83743683b95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180129%2F640_5505a50684d1a927f7f7a83743683b95.jpg&h=02f73f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國天津第一塊IMAX銀幕，昨天傳出被觀眾劃破。據悉，這塊銀幕自加拿大運到天津，原價加上運費至少要40萬至60萬元人民幣（約184萬至276萬元台幣），消息傳出後引發眾怒。<br />\n <br />\n新浪娛樂報導，這塊IMAX銀幕位於天津中影國際影城津灣廣場店被劃壞，工作人員表示對螢幕損壞的原因還不清楚，目前只是在進行調查取證工作，但並未透露是否已找到責任人，至於後續將如何處理，會採取哪些措施，還需等待進一步研究。<br />\n <br />\n面對這樣的行為，中國網友討論激烈：「學會尊重與體面，假期到了，影院還是多注意巡場，散場，顧客多注意克制，公眾場所損壞東西是該照價賠償，弄壞之前還是應該瞭解一下價格，不然你真該賣房了。」「給全國所有的有IMAX影院老大敲個警鐘，千萬不可掉以輕心，不厭其煩的要給觀眾講銀幕千萬別碰。」也有網友呼籲，春節將至請大家文明觀影。<br />\n<br />\n不過也有觀眾表示，這塊IMAX當年是在《阿凡達》電影上映前引進的，也說不定是老化而損壞，「單方面說法還有待查證」。　（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180129/640_0187c2005b71ca7f5ca0f3b75daadcda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180129%2F640_0187c2005b71ca7f5ca0f3b75daadcda.jpg&h=c2fa82c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180129/1287799/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180129%2F1287799%2F&d=3KzxbqbK1C1eIfptp3XcyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e3d09d74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180129%2F1287799%2F&h=01c9c05b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180129/1287799/</a>"},{"pid":"732f515e99f2ad4f4cbb0bc768ce9524688ab865","tid":544122,"uid":75969,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"也有網友呼籲，春節將至請大家文明觀影。<br />\n<br />\n同中國人講文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdde7df62b667964e4eab8a0aa15e0fa873adb8","tid":544122,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"用外國野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44d318461600e1858d0d638fbf403a68bd5e882","tid":544122,"uid":3773,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:18:33.000Z","msg":"中國人不看洋鬼子發明的電影 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要看就看中國戲劇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ae6e52b68c69230336df7d32fea99d0fe4ae8b","tid":544122,"uid":3549,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"比佢地睇用投影機+白紙得啦 洗撚買咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358f3308900d7bc6c26153dda6bb95726b027e87","tid":544122,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"笑哂"},{"pid":"31af9486fc59248b607b15179c08d56dc2a666ee","tid":544122,"uid":12021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"474ab6bbfcbe4a2437ab78b2dc8cfbe366a577b7","tid":544122,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比佢地睇用投影機+白紙得啦 洗撚買咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔知咩人會入場睇。<br />\n中國一線城市普通工都係搵～4000 。<br />\n一張戲飛要幾十。"},{"pid":"9c43fb4003cfd2fdd0c71f2dcaa8851bee2af0d3","tid":544122,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"淘寶咪有囉千<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a63b7ff172b36bcd81635048901adae524be362","tid":544122,"uid